<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA46">
<l>nāṉkūṟuṅ kūṟṟava tittaṉaiyē nāṇāḷun</l>
<l>tēṅkōta nīruruvaṉ ceṅkaṇmā ṉīṅkāta</l>
<l>mākatiyām vennarakiṟ cērāmaṟ kāppataṟku</l>
<l>nīkatiyā neñcē niṉai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Thus far the words I speak: day after day</l>
<l>think, heart what is the way for you</l>
<l>to guard [us] from joining hot hell, that is the way</l>
<l>not abandoned, red-eyed Māl, he who has the colour of water from the rising flood.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
